column5: Where is a good place to exchange $$$$ at Rainy River? Thanks in advance.

I've always had my best experiences exchanging money at any bank. There are places that offer money exchange, but more times than not, don't give a fair exchange. Try your bank in your hometown. That is where I get mine(in my hometown). Brad
Why bother exchanging your U.S. dollars, nobody is giving exchange. It's on par. It'll probably cost you money to change to Canadian Dollars.
